cast.overview: In modern-day Helsinki, two lonely souls in search of love meet by chance in a karaoke bar. However, their path to happiness is beset by obstacles – from lost phone numbers to mistaken addresses, alcoholism, and a charming stray dog.
cast.title: Fallen Leaves

details.biography: Kaisa Karjalainen (born December 3, 1993) is a Finnish musician and singer-songwriter. She sings and plays keyboards in the band Maustetytöt. In the past, she has been a member of the bands Kaneli and Ehkä. She was a soloist and bassist in Kanel and mainly a soloist in Ehkä.
details.name: Kaisa Karjalainen
